      "content": "helpful links just feel like a distraction. i mean what's the point of talking to a stranger about how much everything hurts when the pain isn't going anywhere? it's not just sadness, it's like... a heavy, permanent weight. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to happen so i can finally stop feeling this way.",
